    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 2nd level, you become imbued with the blessings of the Summer Court. You are a font of energy that offers respite from injuries. You have a pool of fey energy represented by a number of [[/r d6]]s equal to your druid level.</p><p>As a bonus action, you can choose one creature you can see within 120 feet of you and spend a number of those dice equal to half your druid level or less. Roll the spent dice and add them together. The target regains a number of hit points equal to the total. The target also gains 1 temporary hit point per die spent.</p><p>You regain all expended dice when you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
